<h3>Recent</h3>


<div style="float: left; width: 50px; padding-top:5px;">
	<img src="gallery/images/dojo-accessibility-50x50.gif" width="50" height="50" alt="dojo accessibility thumbnail"/>
</div>
<div style="float: right; width: 465px;padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 10px;">
<h3>Dojo Accessibility</h3>
<p><a href="gallery/dojo_accessibility.html">Dojo Accessibility</a>: IBM Engineers collaborate with the Dojo engineering team to make the Dojo core widget set in the Dojo Open Source JavaScript toolkits, fully accessible.</p>
</div>
<div class="ibm-rule"><hr></div>

