</div>
<div style="float: right; width: 465px;padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 10px;">
<h3>DB2 pureScale</h3>
<p><a href="gallery/purescale_software.html">DB2 pureScale</a>: IBM achieves a quick and easy up-and-running experience for a powerful database solution that integrates several products in a clustered environment.</p>
</div>
<div class="ibm-rule"><hr></div>

<!----------------------------------------------------What's new entry divider-------------------------------------------------------->


<div style="float: left; width: 50px;padding-top: 5px;">
<img src="gallery/images/dojoglobal_designgallery.gif" width="50 height="50" alt=""  />
</div>
<div style="float: right; width: 465px;padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 10px;">
<h3>Dojo Globalization</h3>
<p>IBM teams from around the world contributed to the <a href="gallery/dojo_globalization.html">globalization of the Dojo open source Javascript toolkit</a> by integrating support for language and cultural conventions as well as bidirectional rendering.</p>
</div>
<div class="ibm-rule"><hr></div>

<!----------------------------------------------------What's new entry divider-------------------------------------------------------->

<div style="float: left; width: 50px;padding-top: 5px;">
<img src="gallery/images/zosmf_designgallery.jpg" width="50 height="50" alt=""  />
</div>
<div style="float: right; width: 465px;padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 10px;">
<h3>IBM® z/OS® Management Facility</h3>
<p>The <a href="gallery/zosmf_systems.html">IBM z/OS Management Facility (z/OSMF)</a> team creates a new face for z/OS:  To bring mainframes into the 21st century, the z/OS team modernized mainframe management by creating a new web-based interface for the new generation of system programmers.</p>
</div>
<br /><br />
<div class="ibm-rule"><hr></div>

<!----------------------------------------------------What's new entry divider-------------------------------------------------------->
