</div>
<div style="float: right; width: 465px;padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 10px;">
<h3>IBM Lotus Sametime 8.5</h3>
<p>The completely redesigned <a href="gallery/sametime_software.html">IBM Lotus Sametime 8.5</a> lets you set up online meetings quickly and lets everyone participate easily, so you can all collaborate effectively.</p>
</div>

<!----------------------------------------------------What's new entry divider-------------------------------------------------------->

